text: Ikililou Dhoinine (born 14 August 1962) is a Comorian politician. He was the President of Comoros from 2011 to 2016. He won the election against Mohamed Said Fazul and Abdou Djabir by having the most votes. Before he was President, Dhoinine was the Vice-President of Comoros from 2006 to 2011.Members of the Government of the Union of Comoros United Nations ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of the Comoros Category:Pharmacists
